.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Sets a callback for a certain event\&. this is very useful for event\-oriented applications\&. event callbacks will not interrupt each other or the mainloop\&.
.sp
.it 1 an-trap
.nr an-no-space-flag 1
.nr an-break-flag 1
